sections.Storage/Stability:
Store omeprazole oral paste between 20°C and 25°C (68°F and 77°F); 
excursions between 15°C and 30°C (59°F and 86°F) are permitted; 
discard tube 28 days after first opening.47 Store omeprazole tablets 
at room temperature in tight, light-resistant containers. Omeprazole 
pellets found in the capsules should not be crushed.
